<emphasis id="3D4C56DD4CBCD640863AD5C9BB0794AB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A.M. Guilietti</emphasis>
et al. 2430 (HUEFS, K). 
<emphasis id="30315B85AEC63CC14504087956E2BF08" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Minas Gerais</emphasis>
